title: Youth unemployment rate in Saudi Arabia in 2019
summary: This is a line chart with an x axis representing Year and a y axis representing Youth unemployment rate, containing a total of 21 data points.
In general Youth unemployment rate has rose over the Year.
The steepest decrease occurs in between the Year 2015 and 2016.
The highest Youth unemployment rate, of value 33.82 was reached at Year 2006
The lowest Youth unemployment rate, of value 23.18 was reported at Year 1999
